=== NAVIGATION_CONSOLE ===
# id: 92
# title: The Navigation Console
# chinese_title: 导航控制台
# category: Terminal
# mode: dungeon

A ship's navigation console still runs its last plotted course. The destination was a system not on any current chart — coordinates that seem to shift slightly each time you read them. A sticky note on the console reads: "Trust the characters, not the numbers."

* [Follow the character-based navigation instructions]
  ~ gain_radical("车")
  "导" (dǎo) — to guide, to navigate. Related to "车" — vehicle.
* [Copy the shifting coordinates]
  ~ gain_xp(25)
  "航" (háng) — to navigate, voyage
* [Plot a new course using the data]
  ~ gain_gold(20)
  "路" (lù) — route, road, path
